        "Dear Jenna,",
        "How are you doing? It\u2019s been a long time since we met in person. You might have remembered  an event that I spoke with you about. I\u2019m glad to let you know that the event is on board. The event is named  \u201cWork for Environment\u201d which focuses on cleaning a nearby lake and spreading awareness about the water pollution caused due to improper disposal of waste into the lake",
        "I\u2019ve been meaning to ask you if you could help me with arrangements including inviting more people to attend the event. However,  I know that you have been busy lately but it would make a huge impact if you could come and bring along a few of your colleagues.",
        "It is scheduled for the 18th of July, which is on a weekend. The idea behind this is to maximize participation and increase awareness of the pollution caused by the residents. If we make this event successful, I believe that the message will be delivered effectively.",
        "Looking forward to seeing you!",
        "Warm wishes,",
